        <abstract> 
<p>Regarding <hi rend="italic">Cytisus</hi> graft with yellow flowers, CD thinks nurseryman has sold <hi rend="italic">Cytisus adami</hi> to JJW’s brother in place of <hi rend="italic">C. purpureus</hi>. This explains apparent "sport". [P.S. on envelope:] <hi rend="italic">C. purpureus</hi> seeds freely. <hi rend="italic">C. adami</hi> never does.</p> 
        </abstract>
